# Axis / VAPIX integration

Follow `docs/architecture/axis-vapix.md`.

- Capability-driven client: probe firmware/features; no single-model hardcoding
- Dedicated service account; least privilege; credentials from vault/env only
- Idempotent event ingest: dedupe with `vapix_event_key` + `event_id`
- Hybrid: VAPIX events may pre-filter before CV; document fusion in ADR
- Health: track `vapix_last_event_age`, RTSP frame liveness, clock skew
- Tests: golden fixtures in `fixtures/vapix/` (no production camera in CI)
